node.text:
Is your dream suit so unique that only really you could design it? If so, we have a surprise for you! Introducing our D.I.Y. Swimsuit Kit. It comes with everything you need to sew your perfect suit from scratch. Sound crazy? It's easier than you'd think! Link in bio to find out more! 

#jolyn #diy #swimsuit

node.text:
Meet Rosie Murphy, high school junior and a competitive swimmer... who also competed at the Next 2021 Olympic Team Trials 🏊‍♀️ ⁠
⁠
Rosie swam the 200 meter backstroke, where she went a 2:15:92. Rosie plans to continue swimming and academic career at UCLA next fall where she will major in psychology! ⁠
Go Bruins!! 🐻⁠
⁠
Rosie was submitted to us by our @jolynnorcal rep team ⁠

node.text:
“I choose JOY” 

@havenfaithshepherd choose to take up swimming as a way to get active without having to wear her prosthetic legs. By sophomore year of HS Haven had made a splash in the sport of swimming and now represents the US! Head to the story to hear about her journey and shop her LEWK 👙#shopthelook
